 The health ministry is giving an update on the Covid-19 situation in the country. #dstv403Show less  JOHANNESBURG - Health Minister Joe Phaahla is expected to meet with the National Coronavirus Command Council and update the nation. Scientists are producing more genomes to determine if the new coronavirus variant is spreading. The Health Department has been alerted and is in discussions with the scientists who discovered the XBB.1.5 variant. 